{"tid":798952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10幾歲果時 以為永遠都唔會老 但家下就30","createTime":"2018-08-29T16:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T19:25:35.000Z","uid":174684,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a58473b36412ebbaf78bc2ed5ea27b0e6ea2a932","tid":798952,"uid":174684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"就快30歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10幾歲嗰時覺得永遠都唔會20歲 <br />\n仲有好耐時間 日子仲有好長<br />\n到家下20尾 好快就3字頭<br />\n其實20之後既日子過得真係好快<br />\n話咁快又一年 又一年<br />\n之後都好快又到40 50 60 之後就死掉了<br />\n<br />\n有無人同我一樣 覺得時間過得好快<br />\n快得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e13a8a03498bc29730d6905122809cbee01845","tid":798952,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都就快3字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想咁快大"},{"pid":"0c97e968b296f995cb3e0c3f5acd298ccbc982c8","tid":798952,"uid":174684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e13a8a03498bc29730d6905122809cbee01845","tid":798952,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都就快3字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想咁快大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"快得好離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n20歲之後淨係不停做野<br />\n時間就勁快過<br />\n家下又9月 好快又新一年"},{"pid":"da500383d8f3272c0dfd016f8c4d734dc72573e4","tid":798952,"uid":168331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"不要再說了！<img src=\"https://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%